Homepage: https://github.com/russiandesman/us_de_layout_linux

Package: us-de-layout
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, xkb-data (>= 2.0)
Description: German ä,ö,ü,ß add-on for US layout
 Adds a US-DE keyboard layout variant for typing German umlauts (ä,ö,ü,ß) on US hardware.
 Select "en(US+DE) RAlt for l3" in your layout tool (e.g., xfce4-keyboard-settings).
 The original evdev.xml is safely modified and restored on removal.
